# Word Navigation Test
# Tests Alt+Left/Right word movement and Cmd+Left/Right line navigation
Output examples/dvds/word-navigation-test.svg

Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme nord
Set Title "Word Navigation Test"
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[36m➜\x1b[0m "

Type "one two three four"
Sleep 500ms

# Move left by word (should go to "four", then "three")
Alt+Left
Sleep 300ms
Alt+Left
Sleep 300ms

# Move to beginning
Cmd+Left
Sleep 300ms

# Move to end
Cmd+Right
Sleep 300ms

Enter
Sleep 1s
